        "title": "Quantitative system drift compensates for altered maternal inputs to the gap gene network of the Scuttle Fly <i>Megaselia abdita</i>", 
        "published": "2015-01-05T00:00:00Z", 
        "versionDate": "2015-01-05T00:00:00Z", 
